{"tid":385611,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊斯高：「假9」係一種態度","createTime":"2017-09-03T11:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T11:19:59.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a906740c8d1b813d7ad9bcf3a0c8ebd660c780a1","tid":385611,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:00:57.000Z","msg":"西班牙大勝意大利，那邊廂意軍陣營在檢討4-2-4，這邊廂狂牛的無鋒陣亦再成熱話，贏波功臣艾斯高直言那不止是一個陣式，那代表一種團結的態度。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙周六於世盃外歐洲區G組主場憑攻中艾斯高（Isco）梅開二度，以3:0大勝同組大敵意大利。艾斯高賽後以「完美的晚上」來形容：「這是我們迄今最重要的比賽，我們度過一個完美的晚上，我們合理地成為勝方。」 西班牙是役踢無鋒陣，開季於皇家馬德里彈起的馬高阿辛斯奧任「假9」，由老大哥恩尼斯達於中場領軍，有份演繹的艾斯高續說：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>假9？那超越了一個陣式，那是正選出場球員，以及留在後備席球員的一種態度。我們是緊密結合的團隊，這點早已聞名天下。</strong></span>」 這是艾斯高歷來代表狂牛兵團出戰的第21場比賽，這位皇馬戰將已累積入5球，之前入球的比賽是對英格蘭、白俄羅斯及以色列。「我有兩腳射門，就攻入兩球，所以我為自己在這特別的一夜幫助球隊感到開心。」他續說。<br />\n<br />\n何蛇又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449525dfede9b5080a56f0e46dd03bc95471df03","tid":385611,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3eee199b664c4c850186086eb7f3a8c9397c63","tid":385611,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3300e257d2d4f9e6d6e5278c0c8b8b9088aeea","tid":385611,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockq